data.description: READY TO MOVE IN!!  Lovely split foyer with over 3,000 square feet with an in-ground pool, a detached 3 bay garage and an accessory dwelling unit upstairs is waiting for you to call HOME.   Accessory dwelling unit /garage has separate 200-amp service and has its own meter and its own well.   Relax in the sunroom or the covered patio by the pool. There are 2 bedrooms/1 bath on main level with a family/dining room, sunroom attached to the back.  Lower level has 3 bedrooms/1 bath, fireplace and a kitchen.  All appliances in house are new, replaced 2021-2022.  New HVAC heat pump installed in dining/living room/sunroom (Dec. 2021) and blown in/rodent retardant insulation installed in attic of home (Nov 2021).  Garage has full bath and laundry room, new HVAC ductless system (Oct 2023), one bay of the garage is a workshop.  New roof on garage in Sept. 2021. Accessory dwelling unit has washer/dryer, new windows, paint and carpet (Sept. 2021).  Underground dog fence installed on about 60% of the property.   Close to interstates, shopping and dining.
